          "@id": "https://doi.org/10.18129/B9.bioc.smartid"
        }
      ],
      "sc:description": "This package enables automated selection of group specific signature, especially for rare population. The package is developed for generating specifc lists of signature genes based on Term Frequency-Inverse Document Frequency (TF-IDF) modified methods. It can also be used as a new gene-set scoring method or data transformation method. Multiple visualization functions are implemented in this package.",
